window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>How is your parents’ divorce or your broken family affecting you today? </p><p><br></p><p>If your answer is “I don’t really know” or you don’t understand the depth of it, you’re not alone. That’s actually very common. But in the words of one therapist, “When it comes to experiencing healing, naming how you’ve been harmed is about 70% of the battle.”</p><p><br></p><p>In this episode, we unveil a new tool that will help you name and diagnose your brokenness, so you can heal it and build the life and relationships you desire. </p><p><br></p><p><b>Take the assessment</b></p><p><br></p><p><b>Shownotes</b></p>"; 
